# conventions.mdc

- Use lowercase with dashes for folders
- Use PascalCase for React components
- Use camelCase for variables and functions
- Prefix event handlers with "handle"
- Use descriptive names that communicate intent
- Prefer named exports unless default export improves clarity
- Keep imports organized and minimal
- Avoid dead code and unused exports
- Use absolute imports when configured
- Keep commit messages in conventional commit format